<doc id="177887" wikidata="Q5774831" url="?curid=177887" title="History from Below (album)">
<text>History from Below is the follow-up album to 2008&#x27;s critically acclaimed &quot;Ode to Sunshine&quot; by San Diego&#x27;s Delta Spirit. The album was released on June 8, 2010.

The band began streaming &quot;White Table&quot; on its website on May 6.

&quot;Devil Knows You&#x27;re Dead&quot; was featured in the series finale of &quot;Friday Night Lights&quot; on July 15, 2011, and &quot;Salt in the Wound&quot; was featured on the television show &quot;Grey&#x27;s Anatomy&quot;.

