# &quot;Ransom Man&quot; – 4:28
# &quot;Devil Knows You’re Dead&quot; – 3:58
# &quot;Golden State&quot; – 3:16
# &quot;Scarecrow&quot; – 4:07
# &quot;Vivian&quot; – 4:29
# &quot;St. Francis&quot; – 4:23
# &quot;Ballad of Vitaly&quot; – 8:05

The last song on the album, &quot;Ballad of Vitaly,&quot; was inspired by the story of Vitaly Kaloyev.

